.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, social-worker, fisherman, pilot
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, satire, spy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, indie, r&b
4 different pets are kept: ferret, hamster, pony, rat
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, purple, fuchsia, chestnut
 1. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 2. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
 3. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 4. the pilot is on the far right##1
 5. the nurse is on the right of the social-worker##1
 6. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the fisherman##1
 7. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 8. the owner of the hamster is the fan of r&b##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is the fan of indie##1
10. the fan of disco is on the far right##1
11. the fisherman is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Job      | social-worker      | nurse     | fisherman    | pilot |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | drama   | satire   | spy           |
| Music-Genre   | electronic  | r&b     | indie    | disco         |
| Pet           | rat         | hamster | pony     | ferret        |
| Color         | pink     | chestnut  | purple | fuchsia       |

