.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, soy-milk, sprite
There 4 different types of food: garlic, grapefruit, pepper, raspberry
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, indonesian, japanese, thai
4 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, bridge, billiard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, rugby, handball, cricket
 1. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 4. the person playing bridge is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 7. the thai is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the japanese##1
 9. the indonesian is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
10. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
12. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | sprite   | cola      | coffee     |
| Food          | pepper     | garlic   | raspberry | grapefruit |
| Nationality   | indonesian | japanese | chinese   | thai       |
| Game           | scrabble       | backgammon      | billiard     | bridge |
| Sport     | biathlon    | handball     | cricket     | rugby     |

