The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cricket, rugby, snowboarding
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, ship, van
 1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 3. the fan of gospel is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 4. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 5. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 6. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 7. the person driving the ship is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 8. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 9. the dunhill-smoker is on the far right##1
10. the person who's sport is rugby is the person driving the van##1
11. the fan of techno is the person watching animation movies##1
12. the davidoff-smoker is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
