City: paris, san-francisco, rome, edinburgh
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, skateboarding, soccer, volleyball
 1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
 3. the person watching family movies is the person traveling to paris##1
 4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 5. the person watching epic movies is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 8. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person eating apple##1
 9. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
10. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
11. the person watching family movies is the person who's sport is surfing##1
12. the person eating watermelon is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |      4       |
| Food          | apple     | strawberry | eggplant  | watermelon   |
| Hobby         | skydiving | cooking    | gardening | magic-tricks |
