 1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left##1
 4. the fan of electronic is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
